OL,6,G🤖 Model Village 🦾 is for anyone
OL,7,Ginterested in AI, machine learning,
OL,8,Gdata science, deep learning, open
OL,9,Gdata, GenAI, and everything in
OL,10,Gbetween. All are welcome to join us to
OL,11,Gcamp and chat about: 1. 🤖🧠📊 AI,
OL,12,Gmachine learning, DL, statistics,
OL,13,Gwhatever you call it. 2. 📊📈⚖️ Data
OL,14,Gscience, open data, data storytelling,
OL,15,Galgo bias, AI ethics. 3. 🐍🦀✨ Python,
OL,16,GRust, R, or whatever you dig to dig
OL,17,Ginto data. 4. 🎵🎻🎷 Bring instruments
OL,18,G(and/or jokes)! We'd love to have some
OL,19,Glive music jams in the evenings.
OL,20,GWhether you go deep or just dipping
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
